    <item>
      <title>Venue</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/venue/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/venue/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Kobe venue&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/kobe-venue.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TNSAA 2026 will be held at:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;riken-center-for-computational-science-r-ccs&#34;&gt;RIKEN Center for Computational Science (R-CCS)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kobe, Japan&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The RIKEN Center for Computational Science (R-CCS) is one of the world’s leading research centers for high-performance computing and computational science. The workshop venue is located in Kobe, a major international port city in western Japan.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;access&#34;&gt;Access&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;from-kansai-international-airport-kix&#34;&gt;From Kansai International Airport (KIX)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Airport Limousine Bus to Sannomiya Station&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;JR train connections available&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Approx. 70–90 minutes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;from-shin-kobe-station&#34;&gt;From Shin-Kobe Station&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Subway + Port Liner access&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Approx. 30 minutes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;local-transportation&#34;&gt;Local Transportation&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Detailed transportation information will be provided closer to the workshop dates.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
